# ⚙️ 5. Required environment variables (VERY important)

Your pipeline must define:

```bash
DOCKERHUB_USERNAME
TAG
```

Example in GitHub Actions:

```yaml
- name: Set tag
  run: |
    TAG=${GITHUB_RUN_NUMBER}-${GITHUB_SHA::7}
    echo "TAG=$TAG" >> $GITHUB_ENV

- name: Export Docker username
  run: echo "DOCKERHUB_USERNAME=${{ secrets.DOCKERHUB_USERNAME }}" >> $GITHUB_ENV
```

---

# 🚀 6. How to use in CI/CD

### Build only affected apps:

```bash
npx nx affected --target=docker-build --base=origin/main
```

### Push only affected apps:

```bash
npx nx affected --target=docker-push --base=origin/main
```

